						               													<description>It happened.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Let&amp;rsquo;s be honest, we knew robots would take over eventually. The crud really hit the fan in the 90&amp;rsquo;s.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;lsquo;Death Bots&amp;rsquo; nuked all the big cities, then made robots of their own, &amp;lsquo;Clanks&amp;rsquo;, to hunt survivors hiding in the suburbs.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If Death Bots weren&amp;rsquo;t enough to worry about, all kinds of crud munchers are running amok in Wastelandia, the suburban wasteland.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The worlds&amp;rsquo; a hot mess, but you and ur crew are still kickin&amp;rsquo; it &amp;lsquo;old school&amp;rsquo; with some sweet hangs and chill vibes. Problem is, all these mutant maniacs keep harshin&amp;rsquo; ur mellow, tryin to bully you around!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If they&amp;rsquo;re gonna start a fight, ur gonna finish it!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Wastelandia is a quirky, dramatic, puzzly, co-op boss battler. &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    In each game, you'll play as teenage kids battling all kinds of bullies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    When battling, you'll roll dice, then choose how to arrange them among your tableau of unique abilities.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    You have the power to manipulate your dice, but that power is a resource your entire team will share and ration throughout your mini-campaign.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    After each completed battle, gain one-of-a-kind gear that synergizes with your character.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Make it the the 4th and final battle, where you'll need to discover insane, game breaking strategies to stand a chance!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
